            "title": "滬指開市升14點 深成指升67點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段揚升，上證綜指以4127點開市，升14點或0.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報14374點，亦升67點或0.47%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升27點或0.57%，開報4778點；創業板指數開市報3394點，升26點或0.78%。</p>\n</div>",
