        {
            "title": "優然牧業擬折讓8.84%向大股東及投資者配股 集資23.46億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">優然牧業(09858)公布，擬向大股東及投資者配股集資合共23.46億元；配股價3.92元，較該股昨收市價4.3元折讓8.84%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"優然牧業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09858-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"優然牧業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09858-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">優然牧業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以該股前5個交易日平均收市價4.77元計，配股價較之折讓17.89%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集資所得淨額約23.3億元，將用於先進技術賦能及數位轉型，以提升營運效能；償還計息債務並優化資本結構，為潛在收購或投資機會提供靈活性；及補充營運資金並用作一般公司用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15586556-%e5%84%aa%e7%84%b6%e7%89%a7%e6%a5%ad%e6%93%ac%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%938-84%e5%90%91%e5%a4%a7%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e5%8f%8a%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e8%80%85%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1-%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%8723-46%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09858.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 09:15:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "景瑞控股昨被法院頒令清盤 股份即時停牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">景瑞控股(01862)公布，香港高等法院已於昨天頒令將公司清盤，破產管理署署長成為臨時清盤人。公司股份已即時停牌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15586545-%e6%99%af%e7%91%9e%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e6%98%a8%e8%a2%ab%e6%b3%95%e9%99%a2%e9%a0%92%e4%bb%a4%e6%b8%85%e7%9b%a4-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e5%8d%b3%e6%99%82%e5%81%9c%e7%89%8c",
